# Design System Color Rules

## No Purple / AI Accent Colors

The `--ai` (#792fff) and `--ai-foreground` purple color tokens should NOT be used unless the user explicitly requests it.

Default replacements:
- `bg-ai` → `bg-foreground`
- `text-ai` → `text-foreground` or `text-muted-foreground`
- `text-ai-foreground` → `text-background`
- `bg-ai/15` → `bg-secondary`
- `border-ai` → `border-border`

## Preferred Palette

Use the base/neutral design tokens for all UI elements:
- Backgrounds: `bg-background`, `bg-card`, `bg-secondary`, `bg-accent`
- Text: `text-foreground`, `text-foreground/80`, `text-muted-foreground`
- Borders: `border-border`, `border-input`
- Interactive: `bg-foreground text-background` for primary buttons/actions
